<dynamic-primeng-form-control *ngFor="let model of formModel; trackBy: trackByFn"
                              [group]="formGroup"
                              [hidden]="model.hidden"
                              [layout]="formLayout"
                              [model]="model"
                              [ngClass]="[getClass(model, 'element', 'host'), getClass(model, 'grid', 'host')]"
                              [templates]="templates"
                              (blur)="onEvent($event, 'blur')"
                              (change)="onEvent($event, 'change')"
                              (focus)="onEvent($event, 'focus')"
                              (pEvent)="onEvent($event, 'custom')"></dynamic-primeng-form-control>
